timelineEntries.description: Leading frontend development team in creating responsive web applications using React and TypeScript. Implemented CI/CD pipelines and improved page load performance by 40%.
Developed and maintained enterprise-level applications using Node.js and React. Integrated AWS services and reduced server costs by 25% through optimization.
Contributed to MVP development for various startups. Worked with Python/Django stack and assisted in deployment processes using Docker.
